{"tid":871609,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【網上熱話】故障頻頻捱轟　堅尼地城站外塗鴉惡搞港鐵標誌","createTime":"2018-10-22T05:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T05:50:58.000Z","uid":48973,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69271ea47ecfc84f458e4dfc4cec29d009566323","tid":871609,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181022/s00001/1540182000527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181022%2Fs00001%2F1540182000527&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=83e42058\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181022%2Fs00001%2F1540182000527&h=e2a74990\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181022/s00001/1540182000527</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181022/s00001/03ea040cbaa6bbc153918481f58d37c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181022%2Fs00001%2F03ea040cbaa6bbc153918481f58d37c0.jpg&h=c439d992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵荃灣線、觀塘線、港島線及將軍澳線上周二（16日）信號系統集體故障，惹來不少輿論批評。今晨有西區市民發現，港鐵堅尼地城站B出口外一幅牆壁，被人漆上諷刺塗鴉，惡搞港鐵的標誌，引起網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「西環變幻時」帖文所見，塗鴉由惡搞標誌和字句組成。標誌方面，塗鴉者在港鐵標誌上加上「尸」字部，讓標誌看起來與「屎」字相似；至於字句，則以英文寫上「Most Troublesome　Railway」（最麻煩的鐵路）。據網民最新上載圖片所示，有關塗鴉已被黑布遮蓋。<br />\n<br />\n帖文流傳後引起網民討論，有人指塗鴉「完美形容現在港鐵服務質素」、「反映事實」、「遲下會唔會個個站都有」。不過，亦有人批評有關塗鴉心態無聊。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應《明報》查詢稱未收到有關報案，至於港鐵方面則暫未回應。<br />\n<br />\n<em>邊位巴打做？</em>"},{"pid":"0482d33cce962b335119c84508b7d6428de0de88","tid":871609,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cc13d7e1045d601a139030f84682f0f8bc0c6a","tid":871609,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco